items.description:
I mainly made applications on the SAP Business Technologies Platform (ex-SCP), stack: Neo, xsjs, xsodata, hdbdd, SAP Fiori Client, SAPUI5. In that projects I worked as Full-Stack Developer, later I became Team Lead:

1. Application for storing information about wagons, tracking location and checking their current status. Application had integration with SAP Analytics Cloud. This application was awarded at SAP Coder comptetition in 2018;

2. Survey application with different response controls (dropdown, checkbox, segmentedbutton, etc.), email notifications and the ability to attach a photo to the response. This application was certified by SAP in 2020.

Other projects I have worked on:

1. SPA for analyzing and aggregating information about user accounts from several systems: SAP, AD, Mail Exchange, Service Desk system, Lansweeper. Mainly worked onfrontend (Vue.js + Vuetify);

2. Classifier of the Service Desk system tickets (Python Flask, algorithm - RandomForest);

3. Middleware for synchronizing worklogs from the Service Desk system to Jira (Python Flask in Docker container);

4. Application for parsing and analyzing tickets from the Service Desk system for making mail notifications and reports (РНР in Docker container);

5. Scripts for processing tickets in Service Desk system: mass creation, mass modification, etc. (РНР).

Graduation works:

• Application for monitoring devices in the network (Bachelor);
• Application for visual modeling of solid body heating (Master).
